snippet.title: Omega Labyrinth Life / Labyrinth Life - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Omega Labyrinth Life on Nintendo Switch™ and Labyrinth Life on PlayStation®4 are coming on August 1st, 2019.

*Supported Language: English

To stay up to date on the latest regarding Omega Labyrinth Life and Labyrinth Life, please visit the official website.
